window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>The sound of a cord snapping abruptly ends her climb, leaving her stranded as an arctic storm bears down. Can her fated mate reach her in time?</i></b></p> <p>Nicole is done with men. After her husband traded her in for a younger model, she built a life on her own terms, strong, independent, and thriving. She might still be curvy, but she’s healthier than ever and determined to conquer Pyramid Mountain as her next solo adventure. But the gruff, know-it-all Forest Ranger insists she’s in over her head. Too bad for him, she doesn’t take orders from anyone.</p> <p>Asher Wells has finally found his fated mate, and she’s as stubborn as she is stunning. She refuses to listen to reason, even with an arctic storm closing in. When she sets out on her dangerous climb, all he can do is slip an emergency beacon into her pack and pray she doesn’t need it.</p> <p>Then the signal goes off.</p> <p>With time running out, Asher races against the elements to reach Nicole before the storm, and the mountain, claim her.</p> <p>Welcome to Mystic River, Alaska, a hidden haven for shifters, where fated mates, fierce passion, and wild adventure await.</p>"; 
